Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.20,0:00:09.26,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 家裡人都睡了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.05,0:00:19.06,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你過來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.30,0:00:25.24,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你說實話 你最近到底在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.98,0:00:28.87,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,都說了 我是讓別人給我一對一補習
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.06,0:00:30.62,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,或者住在朋友家裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.63,0:00:32.52,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我讓你說實話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.04,0:00:35.72,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你晚上 你晚上是去到處瞎逛了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.49,0:00:37.92,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,還是老實說了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.35,0:00:41.58,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然詩子小姐讓我說謊 但看來是不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.62,0:00:44.71,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.08,0:00:46.64,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒有晚上出去亂逛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.07,0:00:49.76,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我是去工作了 在酒吧當調酒師
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.16,0:00:54.41,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,給我差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.59,0:00:56.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要說這種莫名其妙的謊話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.49,0:00:57.64,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.09,0:00:59.97,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.01,0:01:04.31,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是在做見不得光的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.87,0:01:06.95,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽…
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,OP
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.73,0:01:13.20,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}どれだけ離れているのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.30,0:01:20.30,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}君の面影思い出す　ふとした時に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.02,0:01:41.38,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}思い出の中　微笑んでるその横顔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.70,0:01:47.11,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}何気ない日々が　大切なんだと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.32,0:01:51.91,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}思う気持ち　それに今気付いたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.07,0:01:54.72,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}君と笑って過ごした日
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.72,0:01:57.53,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}君と言い合って泣いた日
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.55,0:02:01.89,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}君と過ごした日々　愛しい日々
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.17,0:02:04.66,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}大切だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.39,0:02:10.09,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}ねえ　どれだけ離れているのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.44,0:02:16.34,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}君の温もり思い出しているよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.42,0:02:21.15,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}遠くに見えるあの街の灯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.24,0:02:25.64,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}君は笑えてるかな
Comment: 0,0:00:39.20,0:00:39.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.73,0:01:13.20,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}我們究竟相距多遠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.30,0:01:20.30,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}偶然一瞬 想起了你的容貌模樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.02,0:01:41.38,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}在記憶之中 你微笑著的側臉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.70,0:01:47.11,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}平淡無奇的日常 是無可替的寶物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.32,0:01:51.91,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}這份思念之情 現在終於意識到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.07,0:01:54.72,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}和你歡笑度過的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.72,0:01:57.53,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}和你爭論淚流的曾經
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.55,0:02:01.89,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}我們攜手的每一天 令人無比憐愛的每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.17,0:02:04.66,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}十分珍惜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.39,0:02:10.09,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}我們究竟相距多遠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.44,0:02:16.34,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}我又回憶起你的溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.42,0:02:21.15,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}遙遙可見的那條街道的燈火
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.24,0:02:25.64,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}你正展露著笑容嗎
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,——OP——
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.51,0:02:42.97,hinamatsuri_guochang,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(960,960)\an8}第十話 如同川流
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.71,0:02:41.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想再待在家裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.08,0:02:42.74,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我想離家出走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.50,0:02:45.25,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我媽根本不相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.62,0:02:47.35,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我把存摺當我工作的證據拿給她看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.37,0:02:50.28,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,她居然還說我是不是去賣身了 莫名其妙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.30,0:02:51.09,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那是當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.98,0:02:52.87,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那就出走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.19,0:02:55.34,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,離家出走也挺好的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.70,0:02:57.60,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也經常這麼幹的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.01,0:03:00.95,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但你跟我不同的是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.73,0:03:03.66,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你現在已經是一個有工作領薪水
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.78,0:03:05.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,獨當一面的女人了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.29,0:03:07.63,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,朝著自由前進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.00,0:03:11.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我那個時候 最後就只能回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.73,0:03:14.02,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一直悔恨至今 所以請把我那一份任性活出來…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.02,0:03:15.21,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 詩子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.30,0:03:17.05,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,幹嘛在這裡教壞人家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.00,0:03:18.94,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,已經回不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.71,0:03:22.67,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經賣不出瞳不在的時候的營業額了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.68,0:03:25.15,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我究竟是喜歡她哪一點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.12,0:03:30.82,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我要離家出走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.98,0:03:32.37,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,說得好 瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.97,0:03:36.35,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是離家出走之後該怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.56,0:03:39.25,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,當然 我已經有計劃了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.70,0:03:41.60,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,全都交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.26,0:03:48.37,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這兒就是你以後住的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.65,0:03:50.80,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這兒還是帶家具的房子 馬上就能住哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.97,0:03:53.53,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是這兒 到底要多少錢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.82,0:03:56.39,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,其實是要月租三十萬的 但現在半價就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.71,0:03:58.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,保證金跟酬謝金什麼的不用交了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.69,0:04:00.31,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但還是得要15萬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.45,0:04:02.06,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我可能還是住不起啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.15,0:04:06.54,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,確實是啊 但經我手的房子沒有比這個更便宜的了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.67,0:04:10.06,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼豪華的地方只要15萬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.18,0:04:13.13,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,而且還是拎包入住自帶家具 這種機會一般可是沒有的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.89,0:04:16.81,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,而且你沒有今天可以立馬入住的地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.25,0:04:19.67,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只要在這張合同上簽字 就可以住了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.99,0:04:24.79,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧 是時候離開那個不能理解你的家長了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.27,0:04:30.89,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,把熟人都逼入絕境
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.97,0:04:32.84,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,她真是比黑道還髒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.20,0:04:35.49,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你現在一個人住了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.99,0:04:38.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你現在是在賺大學的學費吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.92,0:04:39.62,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.89,0:04:41.54,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一個人很辛苦的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.85,0:04:43.28,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.69,0:04:45.27,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要是一直這樣的話確實有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.42,0:04:47.13,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那 來我們這裡兼職吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.65,0:04:49.38,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得你能幹得很好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.24,0:04:51.07,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.78,0:04:54.76,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就是一點體力活 沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.34,0:04:57.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,相應地 給的錢也會多一些
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.02,0:04:59.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好 那咱們開始幹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.12,0:05:06.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好怕啊 要是不趕快幹完的話我就要暈過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.11,0:05:12.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要快 要快 要快……
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.30,0:05:19.85,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我手下人跟我說 瞳幹活很麻利啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.76,0:05:23.01,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要是這樣的話小瞳 你也來我們這兒幹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.70,0:05:25.03,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.25,0:05:26.02,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我們怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.36,0:05:27.65,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼一下子都這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.68,0:05:29.21,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了 小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.30,0:05:32.33,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,最近的小年輕有很多都不頂用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.84,0:05:34.32,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,來我們這吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.38,0:05:35.70,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也來我們這兒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.83,0:05:37.31,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我們會多給你點工資的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.03,0:05:57.55,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是你來扮演可疑人物嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.88,0:05:58.75,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.56,0:06:01.29,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.05,0:06:04.18,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,難道你們是「CENTRAL PARK」的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.66,0:06:03.15,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Angel！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.30,0:06:06.32,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.48,0:06:07.74,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 我是你們的歌迷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.82,0:06:10.41,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然沒去過演唱會 但買過你們的CD
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.53,0:06:11.29,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.97,0:06:13.56,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你們怎麼會在這裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.44,0:06:16.60,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我們現在已經停止活動了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.94,0:06:17.61,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.16,0:06:20.67,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為了去美國學習魔術
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.40,0:06:22.32,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.92,0:06:24.93,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,時間差不多了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.26,0:06:26.13,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那請多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.85,0:06:28.21,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.94,0:06:31.82,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,必殺！危險歐拉抖M踢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.83,0:06:33.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.94,0:06:41.75,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那就按我剛才說的做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.01,0:06:44.75,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 還有這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.19,0:06:46.22,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.25,0:06:47.94,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.37,0:06:51.68,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你看到了嗎 今天來的那個叫三島的小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.83,0:06:54.15,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,還特意寫筆記來吸引注意力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.41,0:06:56.77,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為了讓女頭頭滿意真是拚盡全力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.80,0:06:58.22,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,可她就是個派遣社員啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.44,0:07:00.66,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,而且什麼嘛那張臉 也太稚嫩了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.69,0:07:02.70,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,估計會發揮這張臉的作用到處瘋玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.39,0:07:05.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,跟蘿莉控變態一起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.62,0:07:18.17,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}因此呢 生剝鬼節來自一個生剝鬼的節日
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.50,0:07:17.94,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,時間表排得滿滿的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.16,0:07:24.28,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 沒辦法在家裡學習
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.89,0:07:30.03,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就要在這裡學好才行…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.91,0:07:32.84,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你看那個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.70,0:07:41.01,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是少見啊 三島居然上課睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.13,0:07:41.76,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.07,0:07:43.46,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是遊戲打過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.64,0:07:44.57,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那不就是你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.51,0:07:47.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,能舒服地生活真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.70,0:07:49.76,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是因為工作快累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.26,0:07:51.66,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你看了昨天的電視劇了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.75,0:07:53.25,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是大快人心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.64,0:07:55.68,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要是我以後進了公司碰到了不喜歡的女生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.83,0:07:56.94,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要跟她一決高下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.81,0:07:58.69,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.45,0:08:00.94,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不會是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.21,0:08:04.17,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為公司就是一個社會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.29,0:08:07.70,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,三島 我不是告訴過你去複印一下這個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.83,0:08:10.18,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.15,0:08:13.40,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,她根本就沒說過
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.45,0:08:14.58,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.23,0:08:16.89,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這是複印件
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.40,0:08:18.80,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,吃點這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.88,0:08:20.60,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.14,0:08:23.93,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不就是最近很火的那家點心的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.69,0:08:27.04,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我之前碰巧路過這家店
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.55,0:08:29.80,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,各位休息的時候請嘗一嘗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.54,0:08:34.84,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,志保你之前不是說想吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.84,0:08:35.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.42,0:08:42.03,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只是偶爾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.87,0:08:45.97,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 你們誰去把那份資料…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.15,0:08:47.71,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那個我已經整理完了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.91,0:08:51.81,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 這兒我還有一個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.07,0:08:56.28,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要休息下嗎 到時問我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.25,0:09:04.15,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你好像幹了不少工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.53,0:09:05.32,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.39,0:09:06.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是身上背著債嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.07,0:09:08.65,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.99,0:09:10.62,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不想說就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.84,0:09:12.37,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你應該養著小白臉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.53,0:09:14.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.75,0:09:18.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一般新人 剛被欺負馬上就不幹了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.72,0:09:20.03,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然也有人忍著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.03,0:09:24.27,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,能爬上去的可能就是這種人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.79,0:09:26.20,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你要努力哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.60,0:09:27.02,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.83,0:09:29.03,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,朝霧小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.06,0:09:32.89,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你還沒回答我的問題啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.64,0:09:40.83,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在倒是很想看看非半價的食材了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.97,0:09:42.85,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.15,0:09:45.04,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,瞳 你到底在哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.22,0:09:47.51,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在一個人住 沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.66,0:09:50.68,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在剛剛下班回來 很累
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.88,0:09:51.58,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我先掛了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.67,0:09:52.44,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,等下 瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.13,0:09:57.46,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就差一點 就差一點就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.73,0:09:58.60,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.45,0:10:13.24,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 難道說我睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.09,0:10:16.52,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,沒放進冰箱裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.78,0:10:18.39,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,西服上也全是褶皺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.93,0:10:20.35,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,必須要去下一個工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.90,0:10:29.61,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼… 眼淚就止不住了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.53,0:10:32.79,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經到極限了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.54,0:10:35.89,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼我就是不能直接拒絕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.79,0:10:37.85,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是個廢物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.37,0:10:40.17,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,瞳 你聽我剛才說的了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.98,0:10:42.01,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.17,0:10:44.71,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,去你的公寓舉辦一個慶祝搬家的派對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.21,0:10:47.53,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你搬家這麼久也差不多穩定下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.24,0:10:49.84,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,根本就沒穩定下來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.10,0:10:52.27,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣我還必須做派對的準備
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.08,0:10:54.77,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也經常受你的照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.16,0:10:56.43,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,請讓我們去祝賀一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.46,0:10:58.72,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,她房子大得很 大家應該都能來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.04,0:11:02.19,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,您的代基里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.25,0:11:07.25,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經不行了 我只想重新做一個普通女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.73,0:11:09.04,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.28,0:11:11.28,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就算您不理解我也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.30,0:11:13.24,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.62,0:11:20.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 要是能把媽媽請到聚會上的話就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.50,0:11:23.71,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話 她一定會把聚會搞得一塌糊塗的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.44,0:11:27.96,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,解放了 這樣我就解放了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.55,0:11:35.51,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這到底是怎麼一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.16,0:11:38.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到瞳居然會把自己媽媽都邀請過來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.38,0:11:43.37,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,完了 我的店…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.53,0:11:44.62,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你做過頭了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.94,0:11:46.35,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就算被告也不奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.63,0:11:47.40,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.82,0:11:53.20,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這位是 瞳的母親啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.75,0:11:55.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我的名片
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.21,0:11:56.92,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.36,0:12:00.03,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Regular\bord0\frz13.5\pos(614,260)\c&H606264&\3c&HFFFFFF&}芒果有限公司
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.49,0:11:59.87,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這個人脈是怎麼回事！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.69,0:12:02.55,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是還有相當一部分是知名企業的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.13,0:12:06.29,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,瞳的工作能力真的是相當出色啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.47,0:12:07.41,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我十分敬佩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.82,0:12:09.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我是人事部的負責人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.09,0:12:12.21,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,想請她務必加入我們公司呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.37,0:12:14.35,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是瞳的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.55,0:12:17.90,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,工作也不需要找了 直接來我們這就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.31,0:12:20.64,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,她正是未來的幹部候補啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.98,0:12:23.27,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就是現在啊媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.66,0:12:26.60,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,趕快乾脆利落地跟他們說我女兒還只是個中學生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.03,0:12:27.53,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.75,0:12:28.63,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.07,0:12:30.67,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,快說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.13,0:12:32.75,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我女兒就拜託你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.84,0:12:35.80,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.97,0:12:39.72,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你為什麼不說出實話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.95,0:12:43.01,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,進入這種有名企業的門路可不是想要就有的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.45,0:12:46.95,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,而且這不都是你考慮過的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.42,0:12:49.63,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在酒吧工作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.69,0:12:51.82,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,建立與各行業的人脈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.04,0:12:55.05,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,然後選出以最高價錢僱傭自己的地方不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.60,0:12:56.14,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.79,0:12:57.85,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你是我的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.91,0:12:59.63,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽我稍微嚇了一跳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.62,0:13:04.71,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你讓我見識到這份行動力後
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.11,0:13:08.52,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽我也沒辦法開口制止你了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.60,0:13:10.93,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 你呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.50,0:13:12.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就隨你高興地去做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.13,0:13:15.34,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不明所以了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.95,0:13:16.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.89,0:13:20.63,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好了好了 作為主角的你不乾杯的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.70,0:13:22.22,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,派對就沒辦法開始啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.83,0:13:24.65,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.57,0:13:26.12,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.32,0:13:26.97,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.05,0:13:28.89,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,乾杯！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.35,0:13:46.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,結果我到底…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.46,0:13:48.22,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,想要做什麼呢
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.14,0:13:52.14,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,來 這個給你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.27,0:13:56.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是至今為止你工作相應的零花錢哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.46,0:14:01.22,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 明明又讓我住在這裡還管飯了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.37,0:14:02.08,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.53,0:14:05.17,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不要在意 去買喜歡的東西或者拿去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.69,0:14:13.29,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,多麼大的一筆錢啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.61,0:14:33.31,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要給瞳看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.36,0:14:34.13,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.68,0:14:36.45,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我覺得你肯定會嚇一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.64,0:14:38.61,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不過因為是瞳所以我才給你看的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.03,0:14:40.40,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.97,0:14:44.19,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧嚇了一跳了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.42,0:14:45.40,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.92,0:14:46.45,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.37,0:14:53.50,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為5000日元是一大筆錢啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.80,0:14:54.62,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,會嚇一跳…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.58,0:14:57.72,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害啊杏子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.80,0:15:00.18,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我驚嚇過度 都沒反應過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.34,0:15:02.87,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我就說嘛 瞳你真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.11,0:15:06.05,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼反倒是我不得不被嚇一跳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.77,0:15:08.35,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,然後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.75,0:15:12.15,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,叔叔他們跟我說拿去玩或者買東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.77,0:15:15.09,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我不知道怎麼花
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.10,0:15:20.21,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,把那個拋滾出去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.43,0:15:22.77,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,儘可能地讓更多的瓶子倒地的一方就贏了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.23,0:15:25.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是這個的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.01,0:15:27.45,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在公園把蘑菇排好用球撞倒不就行了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.11,0:15:30.57,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\b1\fs80\shad0\bord2.5\blur4\c&H982DEB&\3c&HF4D854&\fn思源黑体 CN Regular}卡拉ok
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.11,0:15:29.90,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那這個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.92,0:15:32.19,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在廁所唱不就行了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.00,0:15:34.54,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在公園喝水不就行了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.53,0:15:38.76,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,有喜歡的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.73,0:15:42.43,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,並沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.39,0:15:45.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那不花錢也沒所謂了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.11,0:15:50.71,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在百貨商場買的東西會那樣包裝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.01,0:15:52.16,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那個是禮物噢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.54,0:15:53.12,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,禮物？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.14,0:15:56.60,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,送給你重要的人的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.85,0:15:58.71,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,飽含了感謝之情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.32,0:16:03.56,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我決定了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.35,0:16:06.52,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord9\fn思源黑体 CN Regular\c&H9680D5&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(1204,100)}告別肩膀酸痛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.35,0:16:06.52,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord5\fn思源黑体 CN Regular\c&HF9F4F5&\3c&HCCBC71&\pos(1514,328)}讓你不知肩酸\N為何物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.35,0:16:06.52,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord5\fn思源黑体 CN Regular\c&HF9F4F5&\3c&HCCBC71&\pos(596,646)}對肩膀酸痛有奇效
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.48,0:16:08.40,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這個的話錢不夠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.64,0:16:10.07,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那要不要換一個？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.80,0:16:13.84,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,叔叔他們一直都在說肩膀酸痛得不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.21,0:16:15.52,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我想把這個當作禮物給他們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.35,0:16:18.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,平時都被他們照顧得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.38,0:16:21.86,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想傳達感謝之情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.23,0:16:24.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是個好孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.15,0:16:26.68,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,慘了 我什麼都沒做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.61,0:16:29.66,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣的話 不夠的錢我來…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.71,0:16:30.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我聽到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.66,0:16:33.65,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 跟班先生 你為什麼在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.67,0:16:35.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,來買慰問品給我爸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.90,0:16:36.96,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,腳底按摩器
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.85,0:16:39.40,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,然後 你的錢不夠吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.71,0:16:40.58,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.85,0:16:42.55,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我打算幫她墊付…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.58,0:16:43.97,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,用別人的錢買禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.14,0:16:45.95,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,心意不夠啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.70,0:16:47.89,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那要怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.31,0:16:50.25,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.45,0:16:54.28,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,錢不夠的話 讓它增加不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.30,0:16:59.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是幹嘛的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.39,0:17:02.33,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,通過跑馬比賽賭錢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.47,0:17:04.31,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,賭中就能賺錢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.80,0:17:06.38,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}夢幻之地 賽馬場
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.13,0:17:07.76,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 等等 等等！！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.25,0:17:10.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算讓杏子幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.54,0:17:11.79,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.85,0:17:13.53,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,馬票由我替她去買
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.57,0:17:14.83,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,重點不是那吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.26,0:17:16.22,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.23,0:17:19.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我還想著說跟班先生是大人 所以能幫到杏子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.27,0:17:23.58,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 真的有信得過的大人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.53,0:17:25.88,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是沒有嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.20,0:17:30.06,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,杏子 不能用通過賭錢賺來的錢去買禮物哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.28,0:17:32.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}知道了嗎 我說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.42,0:17:31.02,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.35,0:17:32.89,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,錢是沒有貴賤之分的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.53,0:17:34.46,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 杏子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.91,0:17:38.56,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,假如你的心意是真的 賽馬之神一定會回應你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.26,0:17:40.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.95,0:17:46.03,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我要賭！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.20,0:17:50.95,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我稍微去吃點胃藥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.68,0:17:53.60,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,總之因為杏子你這是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.83,0:17:54.70,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,先買單場勝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.71,0:17:56.77,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,猜猜誰是第一名然後下注吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.80,0:18:01.24,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那我買這個「背景目錄」500日元
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.26,0:18:02.64,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Regular\c&H544B4C&\3c&H86E7E3&\pos(256,78)}巨型神鷹通路
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.26,0:18:02.64,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Regular\c&HF3F1F2&\3c&H8AC36C&\pos(224,314)}屏幕色調
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.26,0:18:02.64,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Regular\c&HF3F1F2&\3c&H8AC36C&\pos(216,538)}背景目錄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.26,0:18:02.64,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Regular\c&H5B5058&\3c&H7392D8&\pos(216,758)}特別週刊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.26,0:18:02.64,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Regular\pos(236.4,971.2)\c&H5C4E56&\3c&H7493D9&}玻璃步行者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.33,0:18:02.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是最不被看好的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.98,0:18:05.02,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是贏了的話賺最多不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.18,0:18:07.71,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 杏子你還真是個賭徒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.27,0:18:09.77,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我覺得不會中啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.82,0:18:11.69,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.71,0:18:14.57,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到跑在最前頭的人氣最高的屏幕色調居然落馬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.87,0:18:18.07,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在這裡緊跟其後的背景目錄居然得了第一名
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.35,0:18:21.05,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這可是爆了個大冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.61,0:18:22.66,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.69,0:18:24.79,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是新手運氣的級別了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.64,0:18:27.52,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,單場勝賠率是90倍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.01,0:18:30.03,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我這下就有4萬5千日元了？！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.68,0:18:34.19,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就能買禮物了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.66,0:18:35.43,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.48,0:18:36.28,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.47,0:18:37.65,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,比賽接下來才正要開始嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.81,0:18:39.53,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的杏子是真的有運氣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.88,0:18:42.10,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我有運氣？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.94,0:18:45.02,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有很多錢的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.44,0:18:47.35,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也能買其他別的東西了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.79,0:18:52.15,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不過剛才的墜馬真慘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.41,0:18:53.75,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,大概摔斷腿了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.92,0:18:55.19,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只能被做成馬肉刺身了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.08,0:19:00.27,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那匹馬會被怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.70,0:19:02.49,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為骨折了沒辦法再跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.58,0:19:03.49,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,應該會被安樂死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.70,0:19:07.51,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,別介意開始賭下一場吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.93,0:19:09.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.63,0:19:14.22,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.35,0:19:14.99,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,中了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.94,0:19:16.38,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.12,0:19:20.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼說 接下來就是最後一場了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.30,0:19:22.44,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只剩下500日元
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.97,0:19:25.14,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,最低都要賺個20倍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.35,0:19:28.79,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 人氣第六的複寫台
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.86,0:19:33.52,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,杏子 孤注一擲不好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.99,0:19:35.38,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是我誤會了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.67,0:19:37.93,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在最開始賭中之後
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.79,0:19:41.89,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就生出了想賺更多錢的歪念
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.88,0:19:46.21,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這一定 被賽馬之神看穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.16,0:19:49.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我這次不會搞錯了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.36,0:19:52.82,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,將全部心意注入到複寫台裡面！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.44,0:19:56.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,人氣第六的複寫台！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.67,0:19:59.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,看這氣勢是很難趕超了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.43,0:20:01.16,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.60,0:20:02.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,說到底不過是人氣第六
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.03,0:20:03.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在這樣下去的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.02,0:20:07.45,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 肩膀真酸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.56,0:20:09.81,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,到了這個歲數就很辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.97,0:20:11.23,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.20,0:20:14.23,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,像最開始那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.08,0:20:16.18,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,讓他墜馬的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.88,0:20:18.23,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,使用能力的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.08,0:20:21.85,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,腿骨折了吧 只能被做成馬肉刺身了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.13,0:20:23.56,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,肩膀真酸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.65,0:20:24.32,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.97,0:20:26.24,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只能被做成馬肉刺身了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.42,0:20:27.14,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.85,0:20:28.70,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,肩膀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.75,0:20:29.65,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.98,0:20:31.05,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,馬肉刺身
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.47,0:20:32.87,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,馬肉刺身
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.29,0:20:38.55,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,第一名是暫停開關！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.27,0:20:41.72,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒辦法讓它變成馬肉刺身
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.93,0:20:53.10,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,明明我好不容易想著要去買禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.13,0:20:55.92,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦才好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.99,0:20:59.86,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,杏子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.28,0:21:04.94,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你覺得禮物最重要的是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.86,0:21:11.64,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我有東西想給叔叔和阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.95,0:21:13.21,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.62,0:21:15.50,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.92,0:21:21.92,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}捶肩券 一次10分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.62,0:21:21.64,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.55,0:21:25.14,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,並沒有必要一定要用錢買
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.90,0:21:27.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,最重要的是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.44,0:21:29.61,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是對對方的感激之情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.77,0:21:30.99,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.88,0:21:33.89,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都託您照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.23,0:21:35.63,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就想著說要回禮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.56,0:21:39.62,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這種禮物也行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.13,0:21:44.04,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我們非常高興哦杏子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.18,0:21:45.94,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,現在馬上用用看也行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.55,0:21:50.31,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.54,0:21:52.89,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣 舒服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.61,0:21:56.93,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,上次被捶肩是什麼時候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.25,0:21:58.50,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,下一個是阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.31,0:22:02.58,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,全都用了就太浪費啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.82,0:22:05.38,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣的話會再發行的
